</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="A0DAD699FFB6636FF5C54FDF9405FE20" box="[199,885,476,501]" pageId="16" pageNumber="73" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="E87F8512FFB6636FF5C54FDF9405FE20" blockId="16.[151,1437,152,501]" box="[199,885,476,501]" pageId="16" pageNumber="73">
<emphasis id="DAB45900FFB6636FF5C54FDF963EFE20" bold="true" box="[199,334,476,501]" pageId="16" pageNumber="73">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named after the black mesosoma.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
